content:
I had to leave my Zoom training early on Sunday, before the Slack link was shared.

And is there a different Slack for the Text Team?

Thanks!

Hi <@740904995032924161> we actually have anytime calling here now. You can hop into the <#1242256751445934262> channel at any time and look at the pinned post to get the sign up and receive the dialer link for the current campaign
Text has also migrated over to Discord as well.
Do you have the link to that team's training?
Thanks, <@1276944250491113656>. I've seen contradictory info about Slack vs Discord.
I caught some of the training. Is there a PDF guide on using the dialer?
Hi Dan, Jen is off right now, here's a training video  [Dialer training video on YouTube](https://youtu.be/5FYlZK0essc)
